WebGenie Demo Script

Opening

“Good morning everyone.

Today I’ll be demonstrating WebGenie, an Agentic AI-powered portable browser plug-in designed to transform how employees interact with enterprise applications through intelligent AI agents capable of understanding user intent and coordinating multi-step workflows directly within the browser environment.

WebGenie enables users to interact with webpages, enterprise applications, APIs, and connected systems using natural language — helping simplify complex workflows, reduce repetitive manual effort, and improve operational efficiency without requiring changes to browser core components.”

