(Open Connected Apps Screen)

“The connected apps section demonstrates how WebGenie is designed to integrate with enterprise systems such as:

* Outlook,
* Teams,
* Jira,
* GitHub,
* and other enterprise applications.

These are currently sample integrations that represent the broader extensibility model of the platform.

Through APIs, connected integrations, and MCP-style orchestration capabilities, WebGenie is designed to coordinate actions across multiple enterprise systems as part of a unified workflow experience.”

